    <p>My lip balm of the week is the Naturium Phyto-Glow Lip Balm in the shade petal (it was the only one left at Target). Overall, I'd give this one an</p>
    <h2>8.5/10</h2>
    <p>because it is</p>
          <ul> 
            <li>very moisturizing</li>
            <li>glossy</li>
            <li>a pretty color</li>
          </ul>
<p>
         but oh my god it is so thick!! Maybe I'm just getting spoiled by all of the lip oils on the market but it is a sensory nightmare jesus christ. Also the applicator is strange, for a product so thick I feel like a doe foot would lend itslef better to the product than the flat plastic head, which kind of just scrapes the product off.</p>
